            .</p>
               <p>A second count. For <rs id="t17881022-76-off350" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17881022-76-off350" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17881022-76-off350" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing on the same day, one hempen sack, value 10 d. and four bushels of wheat, value 20 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17881022-76-victim649" type="victimName">
